    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Double wall oven cavity-specific component failure</h3><p>Upper or lower cavity fails independently. Bake element $245-$345 per cavity, thermal sensor $145-$215 per cavity. Shared-component failures (main board, user interface, cooling fan) affect both cavities — quoted at single-unit pricing.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Luxury-Glide rack binding (5-8 year pattern)</h3><p>Full-extension ball-bearing racks accumulate oil film + debris. Clean + re-lubricate $115-$165 per pair resolves ~60%; bearing replacement $185-$265 per pair when pitted; full track set $325-$465 per pair after heat-stress damage.</p></div>
